<h1>About This Hotel Demo</h1>

<p>This is a demo application for learning <strong>ZF2 routing and controllers</strong>.</p>

<p>It uses hardcoded room data (no database) to keep things simple.
In a real application like <strong>kittbg.com</strong>, the room data would come from a database
via Doctrine entities.</p>

